.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
House: victorian, ranch-style, modern, futuristic
 1. the futuristic house is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the dutch##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the dutch and the modern house##2
 4. the fan of metal is the futuristic house##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the argentine is the victorian house##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the dutch is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| House     | victorian    | futuristic   | ranch-style    | modern  |

